> topic gmenu inherits global_commands

  + start
    * <get lesson_number> == undefined => <set lesson_number=1>Choose a lesson by typing a number: 1-1? <set currq=lesson_number>
    - goto: {topic=grammar} <get lesson_number>

//  + *
//  - <get lesson_number> == undefined => <set lesson_number=1>Choose a lesson by typing a number: 1-1? <set currq=lesson_number>
//    - {topic=grammar}{@start}

    // {@q<get lesson_number>}
    // - {topic=grammar} <get lesson_number>

  + gstatus
    - grammar status
    ^ lesson_number = <get lesson_number>
    ^ currq = <get currq>

< topic


> topic grammar inherits global_commands

  + usually
    * <get question_number> == q12 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + sometimes
    * <get question_number> == q11 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + seldom
    * <get question_number> == q9 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q6 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + rarely
    * <get question_number> == q12 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q10 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q7 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + once in a while
    * <get question_number> == q4 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + often
    * <get question_number> == q8 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q5 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + never
    * <get question_number> == q11 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q8 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q5 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q4 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q1 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + frequently
    * <get question_number> == q3 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q1 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + every day
    * <get question_number> == q3 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q2 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + always
    * <get question_number> == q10 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q9 => Correct! Try again:
    * <get question_number> == q7 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + almost never
    * <get question_number> == q2 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}

  + almost always
    * <get question_number> == q6 => Correct! Try again:
    ^ {@<get lesson_number>}


  + start
    * <get question_number> == q11 => <set question_number=q12>The doctor says, "I go to the hospital." [rarely|usually]
    * <get question_number> == q10 => <set question_number=q11>The police officer says, "I arrest people." [sometimes|never]
    * <get question_number> == q9 => <set question_number=q10>The football player says, "I practice in the middle of the night." [always|rarely]
    * <get question_number> == q8 => <set question_number=q9>The salesperson says, "I fight with customers." [always|seldom]
    * <get question_number> == q7 => <set question_number=q8>The taxi driver says, "I drive at night." [never|often]
    * <get question_number> == q6 => <set question_number=q7>The pharmacist says, "I'm careful." [always|rarely]
    * <get question_number> == q5 => <set question_number=q6>The mechanic says, "I find the problem with the car." [almost always|seldom]
    * <get question_number> == q4 => <set question_number=q5>The chef says, "I put lemon in milk." [never|often]
    * <get question_number> == q3 => <set question_number=q4>The factory worker says, "I'm bored." [once in a while|never]
    * <get question_number> == q2 => <set question_number=q3>The nurse says, "The hospital is open." [every day|frequently]
    * <get question_number> == q1 => <set question_number=q2>The firefighter says, "I wear a suit and tie to work ." [every day|almost never]
    * <get question_number> == undefined => <set question_number=q1>The flight attendant says, "We're away from home for three or four days." [frequently|never]

< topic
